description: Least number coprime to n, n+1, n+2, n+3 and n+4.
links: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
prog: (Haskell)import Data.List (elemIndex)import Data.Maybe (fromJust)a053673 n = 2 + fromJust   (elemIndex 1 $ map (gcd $ foldl1 lcm $ take 5 [n..]) [2..])-- _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Sep 25 2011
author: _Henry Bottomley_, Feb 15 2000
extensions: More terms from Andrew Gacek (andrew(AT)dgi.net), Feb 21 2000 and _James A. Sellers_, Feb 22 2000
